00:51:57,865 --> 00:51:58,866
Sampai jumpa.

735
00:52:04,163 --> 00:52:06,541
Apa? Astaga, akhirnya bisa.

736
00:52:08,918 --> 00:52:11,754
Baiklah, mari kita lihat.

737
00:52:11,838 --> 00:52:13,065
NAME: KIM HEE-AE
